# dashboard-app
This project contains the following stack


# Backend Technology Stack:
- Java 17
- Spring Boot 3.x
- Spring Web, Spring Data JPA
- H2 in-memory database (for development)
- Maven 3.9.10
- port 8080

# Frontend Technology Stack:
- React 18 (Vite or Create React App)
- Axios for API calls
- Tailwind CSS (optional for clean UI)
- port 3000/3001

# API Communication:
- REST over HTTP
- JSON data format


# Monitoring: 
## Prometheus
- port 9090

## Grafana
-port 3000

# Logging: ES, Kibana

# GitOps: ArgoCD

# DB: Postgres

# Containerization:Docker

# Orchestration: kubernetes 

# CICD: Jenkins 
- port 8080

# sonarQube 
- port 9000

# Nexus 
- port 8081
http://localhost:8081 